{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":547,"text":"Welcome to \"Five Dangerous Things\nYou Should Let Your Children Do.\""},{"time":5000,"text":"I don't have children."},{"time":7000,"text":"I borrow my friends' children, so --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":9334,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12572,"text":"take all this advice with a grain of salt."},{"time":16345,"text":"I'm Gever Tulley."},{"time":18193,"text":"I'm a contract computer\nscientist by trade,"},{"time":22777,"text":"but I'm the founder of something\ncalled the Tinkering School."},{"time":27436,"text":"It's a summer program\nwhich aims to help kids"},{"time":30347,"text":"learn how to build the things\nthat they think of."},{"time":32949,"text":"So we build a lot of things,"},{"time":34862,"text":"and I do put power tools\ninto the hands of second-graders."},{"time":39006,"text":"So if you're thinking about sending\nyour kid to Tinkering School,"},{"time":42084,"text":"they do come back bruised,\nscraped and bloody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45492,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":47785,"text":"You know, we live in a world"},{"time":49381,"text":"that's subjected to ever more\nstringent child safety regulations."},{"time":53340,"text":"There doesn't seem to be\nany limit on how crazy"},{"time":59431,"text":"child safety regulations can get."},{"time":61800,"text":"We put suffocation warnings\non every piece of plastic film"},{"time":66000,"text":"manufactured in the United States,"},{"time":67658,"text":"or for sale with an item\nin the United States."},{"time":70261,"text":"We put warnings on coffee cups"},{"time":72992,"text":"to tell us that the contents may be hot."},{"time":75743,"text":"And we seem to think that any item\nsharper than a golf ball is too sharp"},{"time":82634,"text":"for children under the age of 10."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84714,"text":"So where does this trend stop?"},{"time":87933,"text":"When we round every corner\nand eliminate every sharp object,"},{"time":92751,"text":"every pokey bit in the world,"},{"time":95668,"text":"then the first time that kids\ncome in contact with anything sharp,"},{"time":100763,"text":"or not made out of round plastic,"},{"time":104076,"text":"they'll hurt themselves with it."},{"time":106000,"text":"So, as the boundaries\nof what we determine as the safety zone"},{"time":112328,"text":"grow ever smaller,"},{"time":113916,"text":"we cut off our children\nfrom valuable opportunities"},{"time":117885,"text":"to learn how to interact\nwith the world around them."},{"time":121000,"text":"And despite all of our best\nefforts and intentions,"},{"time":125255,"text":"kids are always going to figure out"},{"time":126977,"text":"how to do the most dangerous\nthing they can,"},{"time":129056,"text":"in whatever environment they can."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131024,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":132440,"text":"So despite the provocative title,"},{"time":135812,"text":"this presentation is really about safety,"},{"time":138589,"text":"and about some simple things\nthat we can do"},{"time":143342,"text":"to raise our kids to be creative,"},{"time":147922,"text":"confident and in control\nof the environment around them."},{"time":152007,"text":"And what I now present to you"},{"time":154160,"text":"is an excerpt from a book in progress."},{"time":157430,"text":"The book is called \"50 Dangerous Things.\""},{"time":159757,"text":"This is \"Five Dangerous Things.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"Thing number one: Play with fire."},{"time":165158,"text":"Learning to control one of the most\nelemental forces in nature"},{"time":170152,"text":"is a pivotal moment\nin any child's personal history."},{"time":174301,"text":"Whether we remember it or not,"},{"time":176276,"text":"it's the first time we really get control"},{"time":179752,"text":"of one of these mysterious things."},{"time":182420,"text":"These mysteries are only revealed"},{"time":184265,"text":"to those who get the opportunity\nto play with it."},{"time":186670,"text":"So, playing with fire."},{"time":189649,"text":"This is like one of the great things\nwe ever discovered, fire."},{"time":194999,"text":"From playing with it, they learn\nsome basic principles about fire,"},{"time":198167,"text":"about intake, combustion, exhaust."},{"time":202000,"text":"These are the three working\nelements of fire"},{"time":204120,"text":"that you have to have\nfor a good, controlled fire."},{"time":207317,"text":"And you can think of the open-pit\nfire as a laboratory."},{"time":212245,"text":"You don't know what they're going\nto learn from playing with it."},{"time":215284,"text":"Let them fool around with it\non their own terms and trust me,"},{"time":219731,"text":"they're going to learn things"},{"time":221557,"text":"that you can't get out of playing\nwith Dora the Explorer toys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226593,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228315,"text":"Number two: Own a pocketknife."},{"time":231371,"text":"Pocketknives are kind of drifting\nout of our cultural consciousness,"},{"time":235611,"text":"which I think is a terrible thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238398,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241885,"text":"Your first pocketknife\nis like the first universal tool"},{"time":245781,"text":"that you're given."},{"time":247000,"text":"You know, it's a spatula, it's a pry bar,"},{"time":250000,"text":"it's a screwdriver and it's a blade, yeah."},{"time":253000,"text":"And it's a powerful and empowering tool."},{"time":257612,"text":"And in a lot of cultures\nthey give knives --"},{"time":260440,"text":"like, as soon as they're\ntoddlers, they have knives."},{"time":262995,"text":"These are Inuit children\ncutting whale blubber."},{"time":266593,"text":"I first saw this in a Canadian\nFilm Board film when I was 10,"},{"time":270585,"text":"and it left a lasting impression,"},{"time":272847,"text":"to see babies playing with knives."},{"time":275000,"text":"And it shows that kids can develop\nan extended sense of self"},{"time":279000,"text":"through a tool at a very young age."},{"time":281591,"text":"You lay down a couple\nof very simple rules --"},{"time":284000,"text":"always cut away from your body,\nkeep the blade sharp, never force it --"},{"time":288586,"text":"and these are things kids\ncan understand and practice with."},{"time":291576,"text":"And yeah, they're going to cut themselves."},{"time":293614,"text":"I have some terrible scars on my legs\nfrom where I stabbed myself."},{"time":296749,"text":"But you know, they're young.\nThey heal fast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299237,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302570,"text":"Number three: Throw a spear."},{"time":305444,"text":"It turns out that our brains\nare actually wired for throwing things,"},{"time":309493,"text":"and like muscles, if you don't\nuse parts of your brain,"},{"time":315205,"text":"they tend to atrophy over time."},{"time":317595,"text":"But when you exercise them,"},{"time":320824,"text":"any given muscle adds strength\nto the whole system,"},{"time":323405,"text":"and that applies to your brain, too."},{"time":325711,"text":"So practicing throwing things\nhas been shown to stimulate"},{"time":330910,"text":"the frontal and parietal lobes,"},{"time":332897,"text":"which have to do with\nvisual acuity, 3D understanding,"},{"time":338276,"text":"and structural problem solving,"},{"time":341847,"text":"so it helps develop their visualization\nskills and their predictive ability."},{"time":347601,"text":"And throwing is a combination\nof analytical and physical skill,"},{"time":353000,"text":"so it's very good for that kind\nof whole-body training."},{"time":358699,"text":"These kinds of target-based practices\nalso help kids develop"},{"time":364939,"text":"attention and concentration skills,"},{"time":367585,"text":"so those are great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369248,"text":"Number [four]: Deconstruct appliances."},{"time":374064,"text":"There is a world of interesting things\ninside your dishwasher."},{"time":378000,"text":"Next time you're about\nto throw out an appliance,"},{"time":381928,"text":"don't throw it out."},{"time":383109,"text":"Take it apart with your kid,"},{"time":384547,"text":"or send him to my school,\nand we'll take it apart with them."},{"time":387932,"text":"Even if you don't know what the parts are,"},{"time":390228,"text":"puzzling out what they might be for"},{"time":392816,"text":"is a really good practice for the kids"},{"time":396290,"text":"to get sort of the sense\nthat they can take things apart,"},{"time":401756,"text":"and no matter how complex they are,"},{"time":403969,"text":"they can understand parts of them."},{"time":406113,"text":"And that means that eventually,\nthey can understand all of them."},{"time":409212,"text":"It's a sense of knowability,\nthat something is knowable."},{"time":413443,"text":"So these black boxes that we live with\nand take for granted"},{"time":417199,"text":"are actually complex things\nmade by other people,"},{"time":421000,"text":"and you can understand them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423137,"text":"Number five: Two-parter."},{"time":427110,"text":"Break the Digital\nMillennium Copyright Act."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429246,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431556,"text":"There are laws beyond safety regulations"},{"time":435366,"text":"that attempt to limit\nhow we can interact with the things"},{"time":438105,"text":"that we own -- in this case,\ndigital media."},{"time":441000,"text":"It's a very simple exercise:"},{"time":443159,"text":"Buy a song on iTunes, write it to a CD,"},{"time":447588,"text":"then rip the CD to an MP3,\nand play it on your very same computer."},{"time":451461,"text":"You've just broken a law."},{"time":453294,"text":"Technically, the RIAA\ncould come and prosecute you."},{"time":456813,"text":"It's an important lesson\nfor kids to understand,"},{"time":459405,"text":"that some of these laws\nget broken by accident,"},{"time":462905,"text":"and that laws have to be interpreted."},{"time":465675,"text":"That's something we often\ntalk about with the kids"},{"time":468049,"text":"when we're fooling around with things\nand breaking them open,"},{"time":472165,"text":"and taking them apart\nand using them for other things."},{"time":474905,"text":"And also when we go out and drive a car."},{"time":480755,"text":"Driving a car is a really empowering act\nfor a young child,"},{"time":485000,"text":"so this is the alternate --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":488699,"text":"For those of you who aren't comfortable\nactually breaking the law,"},{"time":492664,"text":"you can drive a car with your child."},{"time":496361,"text":"This is a great stage for a kid."},{"time":500091,"text":"This happens about the same time"},{"time":501667,"text":"that they get latched onto\nthings like dinosaurs,"},{"time":504020,"text":"these big things in the outside world,"},{"time":506145,"text":"that they're trying to get a grip on."},{"time":508145,"text":"A car is a similar object,\nand they can get in a car and drive it."},{"time":512923,"text":"And that really gives them\na handle on a world"},{"time":517292,"text":"in a way that they don't often\nhave access to."},{"time":521865,"text":"And it's perfectly legal."},{"time":523519,"text":"Find a big empty lot,\nmake sure there's nothing in it,"},{"time":526193,"text":"and that it's on private property,\nand let them drive your car."},{"time":530000,"text":"It's very safe actually."},{"time":531633,"text":"And it's fun for the whole family."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533626,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":537984,"text":"Let's see, I think that's it.\nThat's number five and a half. OK."}]}]}